{"tid":463129,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"批大學生未畢業便申請公屋　施永青：雞鶩爭食，嗚呼哀哉！","createTime":"2017-11-09T08:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T09:28:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"83fbc9228e2cd3881a7483d1e6fe281b14f985bf","tid":463129,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171109/s00001/3df77bbbe68c1dfd2d81f07c0aaf4a12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171109%2Fs00001%2F3df77bbbe68c1dfd2d81f07c0aaf4a12.jpg&h=4c99bb2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對在港上樓困難，不少大學生未畢業便申請公屋，不過中原地產創辦人施永青於《am730》專欄批評這做法是「雞鶩爭食」，「真是嗚呼哀哉！」<br />\n<br />\n專欄題為〈為何大學生也去輪候公屋〉，施永青指，愈來愈多大學生於在學時期已申請公屋，值得社會關注，認為這除了涉及房屋政策，亦是「教育問題」。<br />\n<br />\n施永青表示，從實際利益角度出發，可以理解大學生申請公屋，但他不認同「鼓勵大學生也去申請公屋」言論，「大學生雖然也有自己的權利，但在資源有限的情況下，應讓有更迫切的人優先」。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，香港現時只有20%學生有機會讀大學，而大學畢業後，他們找到收入較高工作機會應比其他人高，故沒理由與處境更困難的人爭奪公屋資源，「作為一個大學生，應該有自信，將來可以幹一番事業。而不是在求學時期已看扁自己，一早放棄與『黃鵠比翼』，而走去『雞鶩爭食』。真是嗚呼哀哉！」<br />\n<br />\n施永青亦提到「綠置居」政策，指政府首要任務是加建公屋，不是把資源放在「綠置居」吸引富戶置業，否則只會延誤有迫切需要的人的「上樓」時間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171109/s00001/1510213839461\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171109%2Fs00001%2F1510213839461&d=9d9uzMU%2FhGmeLAZeyFS39JzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=6f0ff3f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171109%2Fs00001%2F1510213839461&h=0dc3f0c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171109/s00001/1510213839461</a>"},{"pid":"d10726db4d1049afe629fbc823dba1099d34d0f1","tid":463129,"uid":25085,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:19:48.000Z","msg":"上到樓就唔會申請公屋啦<br />\n<br />\n唔通比貴租 租劏房咩 <br />\n<br />\nBtw佢自己都係地產佬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f6a666264cf8c45fb10178a3171895d7001d50","tid":463129,"uid":10692,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:20:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a30025defc124fd15f417c4c553619ba824279fb","tid":463129,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:20:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ed7af9fc465c7bf368bc0dca16342c642c8e6c3","tid":463129,"uid":51904,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:22:02.000Z","msg":"大學畢業都申請公屋既全部係垃圾"},{"pid":"15115bb7d7f90ce4ac0b00ae8796da37fb3c7b86","tid":463129,"uid":26752,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:27:16.000Z","msg":"有自信就買一張聖誕卡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d42660496f3b7238008bbd533956b4a81362c1f","tid":463129,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:28:29.000Z","msg":"幹乜事業？<br />\n炒樓？"},{"pid":"3d9fba2d96304c0df4dc21407db321d84f9a7698","tid":463129,"uid":60529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:32:21.000Z","msg":"有邊一番事業可以5年內買到樓？"},{"pid":"687f2dca1b69770f1f3db03f19e7324dc7416da6","tid":463129,"uid":25085,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:32:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有邊一番事業可以5年內買到樓？</blockquote><br />\n10年都買唔到啦 佢都無考慮過啲讀水泡科嘅大學生"},{"pid":"a0d1b6f5624d2179638f1a0d14e04fca5126b43d","tid":463129,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:35:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有邊一番事業可以5年內買到樓？</blockquote><br />\n奶共或者偷呃拐騙"},{"pid":"4090e5e6d30d51b7d550a701d6a574096d72bf11","tid":463129,"uid":7391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:35:31.000Z","msg":"施永青渣咪個手勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3919b8b0fa6d3a20bdd8f9a275d1eefa21d578e0","t